  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1215108">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1215108/" class="title-link">对自由市场主义经济的反抗</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1215108"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/lovejordan/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1513718-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lovejordan/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">starry</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2007-09-29"
      class="main-meta">2007-09-29 09:18:33</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1215108_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  中国的儒教思想，与西方和美国的民主思想，有极其重要的共同点，那就是对完全自发调节的市场经济所作的牵制和反抗。也就是说，使得市场经济不能完全独立于人而发挥作用、指挥社会。 然而，两者间的区别也是明显的。 儒教思想，通过“不患寡而患不均”的平均主义观念，通过“君...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/1215108/#comments">(4回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">14有用 / 4没用</span>
                  </div>
